.DT
set_owner
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
set_owner

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_owner -  This method sets the owner of the corpse.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void set_owner(string who,
object thing)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^who%^RESET%^ - the name or short desc of the owner
%^BOLD%^thing%^RESET%^ - the object of the owner

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/obj/corpse.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method sets the owner of the corpse.
It will also set up various other things such as adjectives, etc.
.EP

